443
00:32:59,567 --> 00:33:00,807
Let's go. I'll take you home.

444
00:33:02,047 --> 00:33:02,567
No need.

445
00:33:02,928 --> 00:33:03,888
I'll go back by myself.

446
00:33:04,367 --> 00:33:05,928
